      {
        "title": "Isaiah's Mission Told in Vision",
        "introduction": "As Jotham assumes full control upon the death of Uzziah, the prophet Isaiah receives a vision in which he sees himself in the heavenly presence of God. Isaiah is told to go to the people of Judah with a message which God knows the people will not accept. Nevertheless Isaiah is told to keep on preaching even until their rejection has brought them utter ruin."
